tokens.name: Blake's Secret Meeting
tokens.fullDescription: Memory shows Blake meeting with an unknown figure in the parking garage at 11:45 PM. Blake hands over a manila envelope containing what appears to be financial documents.

tokens.name: Charlie's Phone Call
tokens.fullDescription: Charlie is overheard saying 'The transfer went through. They won't trace it back to us.' Phone records show call to offshore number at 10:32 PM.

tokens.name: Diana's Document Signing
tokens.fullDescription: Diana is seen signing documents dated three months prior. The notary stamp appears fresh. She glances nervously at the camera.
